text:
We're holding a special event in Super Mario Run to celebrate the Super Mario Bros. Wonder launch for Nintendo Switch!

Those who have not yet purchased Super Mario Run can play a paid stage for free every day until 11/30! The free stage changes daily.

http://ninten.do/61829NPRM

text:
Jump into the unexpected and experience a new adventure full of the unfamiliar!

Explore the Flower Kingdom either solo or with up to three friends when Super Mario Bros. Wonder launches on 10/20.

http://ninten.do/61889ay3p

Nhảy vào những điều bất ngờ và trải nghiệm một cuộc phiêu lưu mới đầy những điều không quen thuộc!

Khám phá Vương quốc Hoa hoặc một mình hoặc với tối đa ba người bạn khi Super Mario Bros. Wonder ra mắt vào ngày 20/10.

http://ninten.do/61889ay3p

http://ninten.do/61859spzP

text:
The crossover you didn’t know you needed. The Seattle Aquarium and Nintendo of America are teaming up to bring the Animal Crossing: New Horizons game to life! 🌊🍃

Beginning October 7, guests can enjoy an AnimalXem thêm Crossing: New Horizons themed Aquarium experience with photo opportunities, standees of some of your favorite characters, a bingo scavenger hunt and more—all while learning about our mission: Inspiring Conservation of Our Marine Environment!

This is the first time an aquarium experience like this is available in North America and we’re giving our members an early look at the excitement on opening weekend! Learn all about it here: https://www.seattleaquarium.org/press-room/critter-crossover-seattle-aquarium-nintendo-team-bring-animal-crossing-new-horizons

Additional themed activities are coming soon. Follow along to stay up to date!

#AnimalCrossingNewHorizons #ACNH #AnimalCrossing #Nintendo

text:
The crossover you didn’t know you needed. The Seattle Aquarium and Nintendo of America are teaming up to bring the Animal Crossing: New Horizons game to life! 🌊🍃

Beginning October 7, guests can enjoy an AnimalXem thêm Crossing: New Horizons themed Aquarium experience with photo opportunities, standees of some of your favorite characters, a bingo scavenger hunt and more—all while learning about our mission: Inspiring Conservation of Our Marine Environment!

This is the first time an aquarium experience like this is available in North America and we’re giving our members an early look at the excitement on opening weekend! Learn all about it here: https://www.seattleaquarium.org/press-room/critter-crossover-seattle-aquarium-nintendo-team-bring-animal-crossing-new-horizons

Additional themed activities are coming soon. Follow along to stay up to date!

#AnimalCrossingNewHorizons #ACNH #AnimalCrossing #Nintendo

Assemble a group of unlikely heroes when Super Mario RPG releases for Nintendo Switch on Nov. 17! Check out how you can take on a variety of quirky foes using new features, including post-game boss rematches.

text:
With Nintendo Live coming up in Seattle on Sept. 1-4, learn more about what to expect at the event and when to watch the daily tournaments and pre-show livestream at home starting on Sept. 1 at 2:30pm PT.

Learn more: http://ninten.do/61819RBg5
